      "content": "hey so im living in oslo and the sun is basically gone for like 4 months lol. i really want to maximize my immune system for the winter so i was thinking of doing a heavy loading dose of vitamin d. is it okay if i take like 50,000 iu every day for a few weeks to get my levels up fast? feels like a good way to optimize everything",
